Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The overlapping moments
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We might believe them to be eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The labyrinthine sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Begs for light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The impulse eats away at me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Libido erases my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Into darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a hideous form
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If my human tears have dried
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NOur crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wets our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NWe share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we two live on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking each other's wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Defining each other's life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirsting for love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Dark Side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes three victims now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how long will this string of\N"vampiric killings" go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I never realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As I went on living my normal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in the places I never stopped to notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always there in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Always there, watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to break up with him fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Tsukasa? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about that.\NDon't you have a boyfriend yet, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I don't think I need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can't be like that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I could introduce you to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Professor Ochiai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're his favorite student, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not his favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm pretty sure he's married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut her some slack. Tsukasa is "pure," okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not like you lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes her so different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa is actually responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound like we're\Na bunch of shallow airheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And believe it or not, Tsukasa has...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa. Can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And would you mind showing me your notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Borrowing Tsukasa's notes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Her's are the most helpful,\Nshe knows how to organize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having a hard time getting this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, you have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Professor Ochiai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And quit stealing Taira's notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So where were you heading next, Miwako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are a few companies I'd like to apply for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we have to find jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're such a great student,\Nyou could go for a PhD! You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure. I don't think I want more school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I do like doing research and learning new things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I like college, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You don't have to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get a boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you don't get serious about your future\Npretty soon, you could be in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ogikubo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As the days go on, I usually just go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so my only option is to do my best\Nwith what's in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you figure out what it is\Nyou really want to do in life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vampire Murder\N{\an5}Victim Discovered\N{\an5}Body Drained of Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That feeling I've been getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone is watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is on Hakusan Dori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He left Kasuga Station and\Nis headed for Tokyo University!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim has what appear to be\Nbite marks on her neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the blood has been drained from her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Police! Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away from us! Don't even try!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention all on-duty officers within the jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspect in question has been identified\Nas a Level 3 special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving this to Public Security Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a special case for Public Security Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Public Security Division 5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a name for this suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his escape route?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you heard about the Vampire Murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of them. But they're just an urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And hey, I can hear your show\Nthrough your headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A special on the Vampire Murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your occult obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They found fang marks on the victims' necks and-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of stuff you only\Nread about in the tabloids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You never hear about it on the real news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Must have imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,F Squad has gone on ahead\Nand blocked the target's escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki, F Squad, I copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with one striker, and one doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,On our way to apprehend the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiating information control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Issuing gag order to all police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Requesting backup from the MPD Aviation Unit's EC135.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Division 5 detectives and riot police\Nnow in position on target's escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sawazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's headed your way, just like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you, Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think we'd let you get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This game of tag ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Think he's a first offender?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they get a taste of blood, they never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They lose themselves to the mental high\Nand the sexual rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Human blood is just like a narcotic to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And they get ten times higher\Nthan any human on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,An entire race, born with an addiction to human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me put you out of your misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the one behind the serial vampire murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Those were done by...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsukasa, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's really behind the Vampire Murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, she doesn't need to see that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, look at you, Akimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The next station is Korakuen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's place is pretty far from the station.\NThe next station is Korakuen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's place is pretty far from the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's place is pretty far from the station.\NThe doors on the right side will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure she gets there safely!\NThe doors on the right side will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will. Get off my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't have to worry about it, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What I said to you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew you didn't think of me that way. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to make you feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. If looks could kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, it does help to know that\Nyou don't have a boyfriend, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel like, if you did have one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be able to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ever start to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Akimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be far enough away by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the guy I saw on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He followed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A man's blood doesn't do it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to drink her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Akimura...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what you did. You scared her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are,\Nbut there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never directed my bloodlust at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. You found an outlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned your bloodlust on the three other\Nrandom women you murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told your semen was found\Nat each of those scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about that in front of a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your DNA was a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be following you without the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep your hands off of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can act like a hero in front of your girl, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil, human. Either way, you're piece of trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're better off letting me arrest you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a vampire has raped and murdered a victim,\Nthey can never shake the thirst for that pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're guaranteed to kill again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, you would have done\Nthe same thing to her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been taking medicine to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I even gave myself a sedative earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to take this secret to my grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know human lives are all equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're not equally important to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't protect everyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree, it's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I have to kill other women\Njust to keep Tsukasa safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I have killed Tsukasa\Nto stop myself from killing the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I have died myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. I should have realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not on that leg, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Anzai from F Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've apprehended Target A.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently at Hongo 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sawazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidaka will be there to back you up in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I tranqed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And sorry, something came up. Take him in for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least wait three minutes for someone to-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine? No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. 301, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to forget my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Akimura and I were really good friends\Nfor a really long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I least, I thought we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about vampires is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Biologically, they're extremely similar to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't ever transform,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,even most other vampires\Ncan't pick them out in a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So if he was trying his damnedest to hide it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can't blame yourself\Nfor not knowing he was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But vampires are fighting a constant battle\Nagainst the fear that they'll lose control
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the instant they see human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he really meant it when he said he loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But devils and humans were\Nnever meant to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's what we call vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I cut my lip when you shoved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm getting a little sick of your violent-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like softly melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could have loved each other more like that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance encounter that cannot amount to love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this filthy form is who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these fingers trembling as they touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of fighting together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you without hurting you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You and only you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.51,0:22:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of desiring forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the urges surging up inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, again, I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we're softly melting away...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Next Time
